## 1. Business Architecture Context

### 1.1 Market Opportunity

JBM Electric Vehicles operates a rapidly scaling EV fleet across Indian and international markets, serving:
- **STU contracts** (state transport units)
- **Private fleet operators** (corporate, school, ambulance)
- **Retail fleet operators** purchasing buses for resale/deployment
- **Financial institutions** (asset valuation, warranty risk)

**Problem Statement:**
- Fragmented, manual data entry for duty/trip reporting
- Lack of real-time asset traceability across depots and chargers
- Delayed alerts on battery SOC, temperature, and scheduled maintenance
- No unified warranty or penalty tracking across contracts
- Poor visibility into driver behavior and compliance violations
- Underutilized IoT telematics data

**GOCC Solution:**
A centralized, analytics-driven platform enabling:
- Unified visibility across depots, fleets, and assets
- Automated KPI computation and penalty tracking
- Predictive maintenance and warranty breach prevention
- Driver behavior insights and coaching recommendations
- Multi-stakeholder role-based access (Fleet Admin, Depot Manager, Driver, RSA, RD, Manufacturing, Retail Operator)

### 1.2 Core Stakeholders & Benefits

| Stakeholder | Use Case | GOCC Benefit |
|---|---|---|
| **EV Fleet Admin** | Enterprise-level fleet governance | Centralized visibility, penalty forecasting, contract analytics |
| **Depot Manager** | Daily operations, route/shift planning, incident management | Real-time asset status, KPI tracking, maintenance coordination |
| **Driver** | Duty execution, trip tracking | Behavior scoring, compliance monitoring, coaching feedback |
| **RSA / Support Team** | Roadside assistance, fault resolution | Priority ticketing, asset anomaly observability, SLA tracking |
| **RD / Product** | Vehicle performance analysis, quality investigation | Digital twin, fault trends, predictive models, battery analytics |
| **Manufacturing / Service** | Device mapping, EOL testing, subscription management | Device–VIN mapping, firmware OTA, warranty integration |
| **Retail Fleet Operator** | After-sales service, warranty claims, maintenance booking | Basic vehicle data, warranty status alerts, service scheduling |

